            <thetext>Similarly to webrev script OpenGrok should expand PSARC case numbers
to links to particular case in OpenSolaris ARC community.

The putback comments look e.g. like this:

PSARC 2008/305 strsep() in libc
4383867 need strsep() in libc

There can be multiple PSARC cases in single putback comment.

The HTTP link should span just the PSARC keyword and number, not the
ARC case name.

The default prefix of the ARC expansion should be http://www.opensolaris.org/os/community/arc/caselog/

So, for the above PSARC case the link would be:
  http://www.opensolaris.org/os/community/arc/caselog/2008/305

This is somewhat related to bug 327 since ARC case expansion should be
configurable per project.</thetext>
